# Eval: stray files written by arm agents during a grid run (not harness inputs).
# Legit harness files per task are exactly: task.md, tells.md, skills.md, rubric.md, context/.
# Legit hand-graded results live in eval/results/ (kept). Everything below is arm cruft.
eval/**/.claude/
eval/tasks/*/results/
eval/tasks/*/mvp-scope.md
eval/tasks/*/migration-plan.md
eval/tasks/*/plan.md
eval/tasks/*/*-plan.md
eval/tasks/*/response.md
eval/tasks/*/solution*.md
